{"about_the_game":"<strong>The Hermit Chronicles</strong> is a 1st person survival-horror horror game set in a deep forest. Assuming the role of a hermit, you will have to get food, scout your surroundings, and search for resources to make gadgets. But after the sun goes down, you will have to survive for real...<br><br><strong>Exploring the World</strong><br>There are many interesting and beautiful natural places hidden in these forests. lakes, small glades and thickets where you can enjoy the tranquility and beauty of nature. More detailed exploration will open up access to new resources necessary for survival.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151790/extras/exploration.gif?t=1686927419\" /><br><br><strong>Gathering</strong>.<br>Gather edible gifts of the forest, resources, and make supplies.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151790/extras/berries.gif?t=1686927419\" /><br><br><strong>Cooking</strong>.<br>To beat hunger, you can make more hearty dishes from the supplies you get.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151790/extras/cooking.gif?t=1686927419\" /><br><br><strong>Craft</strong>.<br>On the workbench, you can craft gear that will make your life easier.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151790/extras/craft.gif?t=1686927419\" /><br><br><strong>Hunting</strong>.<br>Food can be obtained not only by gathering, but also - by hunting! Use a homemade bow or traps.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151790/extras/hunt.gif?t=1686927419\" /><br><br><strong>Changing weather</strong>.<br>Sometimes the weather can take you by surprise and make you go back to the cabin.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151790/extras/weather.gif?t=1686927419\" /><br><br><strong>Night visitors</strong>.<br>There are more than just rabbits in these places. It's not at all safe in this place at night. Use your weapon of choice to confront serious danger.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151790/extras/monster.gif?t=1686927419\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Search for resources and build tools to help you survive.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hunting, fishing, and gathering will help you avoid starvation.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore the atmospheric forest.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fight for your life in fierce battles against bloodthirsty relics.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2151790/606903204680e79cc87c79cec2a42240da67fb3a.jpg"},{"name":"The Mushroom Man","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2151790/c46ad0fb47a020008fb31f2630cde783ed644f24.jpg"},{"name":"Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2151790/d17d12966e710b8e3818cf7ce9882d5a820a9954.jpg"},{"name":"Herbalist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2151790/b31df37f09ab5d23f482babbab47b31be71ff691.jpg"},{"name":"Fisherman","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2151790/a267c4a57967b99104de5661e5674039031d0259.jpg"},{"name":"Scrap man","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2151790/dbdb9c16464e63c866778b692b81533dada4cf6a.jpg"},{"name":"AWOOOOOOO","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2151790/c08a0d6430657c9bf005d225afcb957d9e2ae4a4.jpg"},{"name":"Forest lake","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2151790/bcb92871c2504aee91fc9631fc829432ae72173c.jpg"},{